htmlDescription.htmlText:
My townhouse is 2 Bedrooms, 2.5 Bathrooms and the room available is spacious.

Your private bedroom has a queen bed with wireless internet, TV and cable with plenty of storage along with fresh bed linens, towels (bath and beach) and a private bathroom attached.

All house access; Kitchen, Washer & Dryer, Patio, & Downstairs Living Room and TV that also has cable and Apple TV.

Cable and Internet service are free, as are the washer and dryer. The street parking is easy, the taxi to LAX is about $20, and the bus stop is a few blocks away.

There are beach cruisers available in the garage for use. I encourage you to enjoy the 22 mile (35 km) long beach bike trail, also known as The Strand. It is a paved bicycle path that runs mostly along the Pacific Ocean shoreline. The most northern part of the trail starts at Will Rogers State Beach in Pacific Palisades. The Southern part of the trail is in Torrance County Beach. The midpoint between the two ends of the path is your stay here in El Segundo.

I am a very active person, and on the go a lot, so I will schedule myself to be out of the home quite a bit during guest stays. I also have a TV with cable in my room, so I will happily allow guests use of the common space undisturbed.

Just minutes from LAX and a short drive or bike ride from Manhattan Beach, Hermosa Beach, Redondo Beach, Marina del Rey, Venice, Santa Monica, Torrance, and Palos Verdes. Take a beautiful drive up to coast to see the sights of Malibu.

Less than 10 minutes South of LAX
30 minutes from downtown LA.
20 minutes from Santa Monica
30 minutes from Hollywood

If you want to catch the sights at Malibu, it's a beautiful drive up the coast. The Getty Museum, Getty Villa and the L.A. County Museum of art are an easy drive north.

features.title: Booking Protection Guarantee
features.subtitle: In the unlikely event a Host needs to cancel your booking within 30 days of check-in, we’ll find you a similar or better home, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: Check-In Guarantee
features.subtitle: If you can’t check into your home and the Host cannot resolve the issue, we’ll find you a similar or better home for the length of your original stay, or we’ll refund you.

features.title: Get-What-You-Booked Guarantee
features.subtitle: If at any time during your stay you find your listing isn't as advertised—for example, the refrigerator stops working and your Host can’t easily fix it, or it has fewer bedrooms than listed—you'll have three days to report it and we’ll find you a similar or better home, or we’ll refund you.

features.subtitle: If you ever feel unsafe, you’ll get priority access to specially-trained safety agents, day or night.
